snippet.title: Shelly Marie Redmond
snippet.description:
Hi!

Thank you for stopping by our channel. My name is Shelly Marie Redmond, and I am passionate about helping individuals lose weight, balance hormones, decrease blood sugars, and eliminate pain and migraines by following a real world, budget friendly ketogenic, low carb, anti-inflammatory lifestyle.

In this channel you will find fun, real world, budget friendly, and positive videos on the following topics: 
Keto diet on a budget.
Keto recipes on a budget.
Cheap and easy keto meals.
Keto diet for beginners to advanced.
Beginners guide to keto.
Sample keto meal plans.
Keto product reviews.
Keto for migraines.
Keto and inflammation.
Keto and hormones.
Keto and diabetes.
Keto and weight loss.

As a ketogenic and anti-inflammatory dietitian, I love bringing you delicious recipes, product reviews, and mean plans your waistline, pocketbook, and family will love.

For business inquires, you can email us at shelly@skinnylouisiana.com.
